narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take it if you want to learn German. That's all.
Slightly tougher than the L1 course, but overall, fairly similar in structure.
The hardest test for L1 has now become the norm of difficulty for L2 tests! Other than that, a nice, smooth transition and continuation from L1 topics!
Definitely take this class with Will.
It's hard but if you get a good professor it will be fun.
German is a great language program here. I wholeheartedly recommend it.
